Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.31,0:00:04.23,Main,Sai,0000,0000,0000,,You've been having things \Nyour way for a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.97,0:00:07.19,Main,Sai,0000,0000,0000,,But your reign ends here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.19,0:00:09.76,Main,Sai,0000,0000,0000,,Take that, and that, and that!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.19,0:00:11.32,sign_197_4_Ogre,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Ogre
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.76,0:00:14.05,Main,Sai,0000,0000,0000,,Consecutive low, weak kicks! This is a \Nstrategy I figured out so you can't escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.05,0:00:16.82,Main,King,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief. You just don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.82,0:00:20.06,sign_404_8_Home,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Home
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.48,0:00:19.29,Main,King,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to trap someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.29,0:00:21.33,Main,King,0000,0000,0000,,this is how you do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.55,0:00:29.50,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.50,0:00:31.55,Italics,Game,0000,0000,0000,,K.O.!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.55,0:00:33.33,Italics,Game,0000,0000,0000,,Bunny bun bun!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.55,0:00:36.22,sign_404_8_Home,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(190,316.666)}Home
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.55,0:00:36.22,sign_757_14_Dokishisu,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Dokishisu
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.22,0:00:35.55,Main,Sai,0000,0000,0000,,One more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.22,0:00:37.43,Italics,Game,0000,0000,0000,,K.O.!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.43,0:00:39.60,Italics,Game,0000,0000,0000,,K.O.!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.47,0:00:41.64,Italics,Game,0000,0000,0000,,K.O.!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.89,0:00:53.87,Italics,Game,0000,0000,0000,,K.O.!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.87,0:00:55.70,Italics,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Bunny bun bun!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.70,0:00:58.39,Main,Sai,0000,0000,0000,,This is shit! This game is shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.39,0:01:00.20,Main,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\shad0\b1}That's all he could say
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.43,0:01:04.08,Main,Sai,0000,0000,0000,,The heck is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.07,0:01:10.25,Main,King,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, those were distributed \Nto a handful of heroes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.25,0:01:12.59,Main,King,0000,0000,0000,,It's apparently still a prototype, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.86,0:01:17.18,Main,King,0000,0000,0000,,It's a terminal for receiving backup requests \Nand the latest intel immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.87,0:01:19.29,Main,Saitama,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't get one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.29,0:01:20.06,Main,King,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.61,0:01:26.45,Main,King,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Maybe they think you can't \Nhandle buttons and stuff very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.01,0:01:30.15,Main,Sai,0000,0000,0000,,One more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.63,0:01:34.22,Main,Sai,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, I'm going to use even faster \Nconsecutive low, weak kicks and win!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.31,0:03:10.29,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,A message has arrived from \Nthe Monster Association!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.74,0:03:14.08,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,A message has arrived from \Nthe Monster Association!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.59,0:03:17.09,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,He's been taken over by some parasite!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.09,0:03:18.96,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Call all the resident heroes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.96,0:03:22.38,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? This is the west wing, \Nfloor 2, conference room 7!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.85,0:03:22.38,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Should I shoot?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.38,0:03:23.61,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.61,0:03:24.38,Main,Sitch,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.90,0:03:26.53,Main,Sitch,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to the message!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.87,0:03:31.52,Next Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(460,270)\fs26\fad(462,1)}The Encircling Net of Justice
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.27,0:03:31.94,Main,Eye,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}It's a pleasure to meet you, ladies and \Ngentlemen of the Hero Association.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.94,0:03:36.11,Main,Eye,0000,0000,0000,,I am Gyoro-Gyoro, an officer \Nin the Monster Association.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.46,0:03:41.23,Main,Eye,0000,0000,0000,,As you already know, we have the son of one \Nof your top executives in our custody.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.23,0:03:42.45,Main,Sitch,0000,0000,0000,,What are your demands?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.45,0:03:44.70,Main,Eye,0000,0000,0000,,We have but one request.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.25,0:03:49.35,Main,Eye,0000,0000,0000,,We are tired of being oppressed \Njust because we're monsters,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.35,0:03:52.35,Main,Eye,0000,0000,0000,,so we ask that you leave us alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.91,0:03:55.82,Main,Eye,0000,0000,0000,,We are currently hiding in \Nan abandoned part of City Z,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.82,0:03:59.35,Main,Eye,0000,0000,0000,,where we monsters help each other out \Nwhile we try to make ends meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.35,0:04:03.91,Main,Eye,0000,0000,0000,,We would never ask for something as \Nluxurious as living freely in the outside world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.91,0:04:10.77,Main,Eye,0000,0000,0000,,We will never attack another civilian again, \Nnor intrude upon your way of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.77,0:04:16.44,Main,Eye,0000,0000,0000,,All we ask for in return \Nis our own sanctuary.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.44,0:04:19.44,Main,Eye,0000,0000,0000,,Our dream is the realization \Nof a society in which
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.44,0:04:21.98,Main,Eye,0000,0000,0000,,humans and monsters can \Nlive together in harmony.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.98,0:04:24.61,Main,Sitch,0000,0000,0000,,Then why did you insist on rampaging?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.61,0:04:27.07,Main,Eye,0000,0000,0000,,By showing you our power,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.07,0:04:32.98,Main,Eye,0000,0000,0000,,we thought you'd find that you could benefit \Nfrom agreeing to this idea, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.98,0:04:36.29,Main,Eye,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure we want to avoid any \Nfurther casualties on either side.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.29,0:04:40.13,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,So they're asking for a cease-fire. \NJust like I thought they would.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.13,0:04:41.05,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.67,0:04:46.26,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We promise that we will not engage the \NMonster Association from here on out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.81,0:04:49.22,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,So you should release your \Nhostage immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.22,0:04:53.88,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You stupid monsters better enjoy \Nthis brief moment of peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.88,0:04:57.02,Italics,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to take you down before \Nyou can grow any stron—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.31,0:05:01.01,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Whoops. My finger slipped.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.01,0:05:05.15,Main,Eye,0000,0000,0000,,Come, now. We're still in the middle \Nof negotiations, Destrochloridium.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.15,0:05:07.91,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,My bad. I need to work on my patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.78,0:05:10.32,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,He killed him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.32,0:05:13.75,Main,Sitch,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really have any \Nintention to negotiate?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.79,0:05:18.15,Main,eye,0000,0000,0000,,It's so fun to mess with you adults.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.15,0:05:20.78,Main,Eye,0000,0000,0000,,Humans and monsters living in harmony?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.78,0:05:22.67,Main,Eye,0000,0000,0000,,I think that's my best joke yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.02,0:05:25.14,Main,Eye,0000,0000,0000,,You people are even dumber than I thought
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.14,0:05:27.42,Main,Eye,0000,0000,0000,,if you were going to accept \Nthat demand so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.42,0:05:30.09,Main,Sitch,0000,0000,0000,,What do you plan to do with the hostage?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.09,0:05:31.43,Main,Sitch,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you already—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.43,0:05:33.56,Main,Eye,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, he's still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.56,0:05:38.23,Main,Eye,0000,0000,0000,,We took a hostage so you \Ncowards couldn't run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.62,0:05:41.27,Main,Eye,0000,0000,0000,,We'll give you just three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.27,0:05:46.82,Main,Eye,0000,0000,0000,,In that time, gather your strongest \Nheroes and come rescue the brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.82,0:05:52.15,Main,Eye,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Orochi and the rest of the \NMonster Association will be waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.26,0:05:57.16,Main,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,It self-destructed?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.16,0:06:00.54,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,There's still one more left! \NWhere are the heroes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.54,0:06:02.62,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Are we done talking?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.62,0:06:03.50,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.50,0:06:05.94,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I can go crazy now, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.24,0:06:10.39,sign_7523_72_Class_B_Rank_3_W,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(130,180}Class {\fs34}S {\fs24}Rank {\fs34}11\NSuperalloy Blackluster
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.24,0:06:10.39,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Was this the emergency \Nyou guys called about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.39,0:06:15.81,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Blackluster. Thank goodness we asked \Nyou to stay here to defend headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.81,0:06:17.34,Main,Sitch,0000,0000,0000,,No! It's not over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.34,0:06:20.56,Main,Sitch,0000,0000,0000,,That thing's a parasite! \NIt's true form's out now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.56,0:06:22.56,Main,Bug,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are way too slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.99,0:06:27.42,Main,Bug,0000,0000,0000,,This Class S hero's body is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.99,0:06:32.10,Main,Bug,0000,0000,0000,,His body's as hard as steel! My drills—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.89,0:06:35.39,Main,Bug,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible! This is just skin, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.94,0:06:39.08,Main,Bl,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.08,0:06:42.55,Main,Bl,0000,0000,0000,,Of course you don't stand a chance. \NMy skin's toughened by steel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.69,0:06:46.52,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The Monster Association must \Nbe extremely confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.52,0:06:47.34,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.34,0:06:50.92,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean? Our plan from \Nthe start was to rescue the hostage!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.92,0:06:54.26,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You're okay with sending our Class S \Nheroes in, knowing it's a trap?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.26,0:06:55.88,Italics,BL,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.88,0:07:01.00,Italics,BL,0000,0000,0000,,The executives are actually panicking \Nover the Monster Association.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.00,0:07:02.38,Italics,BL,0000,0000,0000,,I should just...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.81,0:07:03.36,Main,BL,0000,0000,0000,,Ahem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.77,0:07:05.94,Main,BL,0000,0000,0000,,Eyes over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.09,0:07:10.26,Main,BL,0000,0000,0000,,How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.26,0:07:13.23,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,H-How's what, Blackluster?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.23,0:07:16.53,Main,BL,0000,0000,0000,,Have you calmed down a little \Nafter staring at my muscles?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.53,0:07:18.62,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.62,0:07:21.83,Main,BL,0000,0000,0000,,We should be just as confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.41,0:07:21.83,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.21,0:07:25.92,Main,BL,0000,0000,0000,,It appears the time has come \Nwhen I can truly shine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.54,0:07:29.09,Main,BL,0000,0000,0000,,I'm more worried about the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.09,0:07:32.34,Main,BL,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hoping I can at least \Ngo all-out on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.37,0:07:35.43,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You think the heroes will show?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.43,0:07:39.47,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you saw what happened today. \NWe're way stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.47,0:07:41.28,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We can probably attack all at once and
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.28,0:07:43.69,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,not even have to worry about \Nusing the hostage as bait.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.08,0:07:49.54,Main,Eye,0000,0000,0000,,Confidence is a good thing, but acting \Non impulse always has its consequences.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.54,0:07:52.73,Main,Eye,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that the Hero Association \Nhas its own kind of monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.73,0:07:56.20,Main,Eye,0000,0000,0000,,Letting them go free will \Ncause problems later.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.20,0:08:00.01,Main,Eye,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we'll gather them all in \None place and strike them all at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.01,0:08:02.12,Main,Eye,0000,0000,0000,,This is what our hostage is for.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.44,0:08:04.10,Main,Eye,0000,0000,0000,,Once they lose all their forces,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.10,0:08:07.09,Main,Eye,0000,0000,0000,,we'll eradicate the rest \Nof the Hero Association.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.09,0:08:09.95,Main,Eye,0000,0000,0000,,After humanity loses the \Nability to fight back,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.95,0:08:14.34,Main,Eye,0000,0000,0000,,they'll be helpless against us and have \Nno other choice but to go extinct.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.34,0:08:15.34,Main,Eye,0000,0000,0000,,And then,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.34,0:08:17.30,Main,Eye,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Orochi will become king,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.30,0:08:21.68,Main,Eye,0000,0000,0000,,and a world for just monsters \Nwill finally become a reality!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.83,0:08:26.85,Main,Eye,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter? Where's my applause?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.85,0:08:29.99,Main,Eye,0000,0000,0000,,Are you not satisfied serving Lord Orochi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.99,0:08:33.45,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We just gathered here to \Ncrush the Hero Association.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.45,0:08:35.87,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,No one said anything about serving anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.70,0:08:40.61,Main,Orochi,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? What's a loser doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.71,0:08:44.41,Main,Bug,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.41,0:08:46.85,Main,Eye,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here, Roach Awakening?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.85,0:08:49.63,Main,Eye,0000,0000,0000,,You have some nerve, showing up after you lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.63,0:08:52.38,Main,Bug,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! I just lost my feet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.38,0:08:53.59,Main,Bug,0000,0000,0000,,I can still fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.59,0:08:55.03,Main,Bug,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, I'll—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.21,0:08:57.59,Main,Bug,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, we're friends, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.59,0:08:59.49,Main,Bug,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! No...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.49,0:09:01.14,Main,Bug,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't! Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.14,0:09:02.47,Main,Bug,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.81,0:09:03.46,Main,Bug,0000,0000,0000,,Don't—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.86,0:09:07.42,Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,He ate him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.42,0:09:09.73,Main,Eye,0000,0000,0000,,That goes for you as well, Super S.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.41,0:09:14.66,Main,S,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm still... I barely have a scratch on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.09,0:09:16.41,Main,S,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't actually lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.41,0:09:22.25,Main,Eye,0000,0000,0000,,Well, her power can be quite useful, \Nso it might be worthwhile to let her live.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.37,0:09:25.06,Main,Oro,0000,0000,0000,,There won't be a next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.06,0:09:28.00,Main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.49,0:09:31.30,Main,Eye,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, if any of you have a problem,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.30,0:09:34.38,Main,Eye,0000,0000,0000,,you can challenge Lord \NOrochi yourselves later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.75,0:09:39.78,Main,Eye,0000,0000,0000,,If you actually defeat Lord \NOrochi, we'll have a new boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.78,0:09:40.72,Main,Oro,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.72,0:09:45.62,Main,Oro,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Gyoro-Gyoro, \NI don't see Goketsu anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.62,0:09:46.23,Main,Eye,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.61,0:09:49.25,Main,Eye,0000,0000,0000,,It appears he hasn't returned yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.29,0:09:52.22,Main,Eye,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll go check things out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.51,0:10:02.70,Main,Eye,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable... \NSomeone defeated Goketsu? But who?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.11,0:10:07.66,Main,Eye,0000,0000,0000,,I guess this won't go as \Neasily as planned after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.79,0:10:10.15,Main,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.58,0:10:12.63,Main,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,Did someone take me out?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.43,0:10:21.10,Main,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,I need to get back to my hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.68,0:10:24.83,Italics,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.77,0:10:30.44,Italics,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,There's no doubt about it. \NThat's the Class A hero Death Gatling.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.47,0:10:35.40,Italics,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,King got me way worse than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.85,0:10:38.11,Italics,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,My body's actually at its limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.11,0:10:40.45,Italics,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I'll just got home for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.55,0:10:47.12,Main,Kuse,0000,0000,0000,,There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.64,0:10:49.21,Main,Kuse,0000,0000,0000,,How does it feel, Genos?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.53,0:10:51.92,Main,Kuse,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it'll work just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.39,0:10:58.13,Main,Genos,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Thank you, Dr. Kuseno,\Nfor doing this on such short notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.13,0:11:04.17,Main,Kuse,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I know you wanted to get \Nright back into the fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.17,0:11:07.60,Main,Kuse,0000,0000,0000,,The changes should be easy to \Nmanage, but with this upgrade,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.60,0:11:10.74,Main,Kuse,0000,0000,0000,,you should definitely feel much stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.74,0:11:12.85,Main,Genos,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I won't lose again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.85,0:11:16.98,Main,Kuse,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to be overconfident. \NIt's okay if you lose,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.36,0:11:19.24,Main,Kuse,0000,0000,0000,,as long as you come back alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.83,0:11:25.21,Main,Kuse,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing you yesterday reminded \Nme of my younger days.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.21,0:11:28.58,Main,Kuse,0000,0000,0000,,I had a strong sense of \Njustice and continued forward
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.58,0:11:31.43,Main,Kuse,0000,0000,0000,,with absolutely no fear back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.70,0:11:37.09,Main,Kuse,0000,0000,0000,,Genos, just make sure you \Ndon't push yourself too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.71,0:11:44.13,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Breaking news! Breaking news!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.53,0:11:51.35,Main,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18\b1\fnArial\3c&H484A44&\shad0}The Monsters Declare War\N{\c&H3D3D32&\3c&HDBD9D7&\bord1}Monsters Infiltrate the Hero Association Headquarters {\c&H3D3D32&\3c&HDBD9D7&\bord2}Leaving 2 Employees Dead
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.13,0:11:45.87,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The Monster Association?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.87,0:11:48.11,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,They infiltrated the headquarters? What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.11,0:11:49.97,Main,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,They even killed one of the executives?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.97,0:11:51.35,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.35,0:11:54.86,Italics,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}This morning, an organization calling \Nthemselves the Monster Association
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.35,0:11:57.48,sign_17056_197_Monster_Associat,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Monster Association
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.35,0:11:57.48,sign_17056_198_The_Monster_Asso,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,The Monster Association Declares War
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.86,0:12:00.46,Italics,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}made a criminal declaration that they had \Ntaken a hostage from the Hero Association.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.47,0:11:59.65,Main,Zen,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bro Bat...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.28,0:12:05.49,Italics - Top,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,According to the declaration, \Nthey expressed that even more destruction
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.74,0:12:05.87,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like the Hero Association and the \NMonster Association are going to clash head-on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.49,0:12:07.86,Italics - Top,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,and casualties would be\Ncaused by the monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.87,0:12:10.38,Main,Chin,0000,0000,0000,,A war? Curse the Monster \NAssociation... How awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.86,0:12:11.29,Italics - Top,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,The Hero Association is calling \Nfor extra security...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.38,0:12:12.41,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,What's going to happen to us if they lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.41,0:12:15.22,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It sucks, but there's nothing we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.22,0:12:16.00,Main,Chin,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.44,0:12:20.46,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,They can win... right? The heroes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.46,0:12:23.34,Main,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, you're not going \Nto participate in the operation?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.72,0:12:26.85,Main,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,Metal Knight! Don't you understand \Nwhat's going on right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.17,0:12:29.51,Italics,Metal,0000,0000,0000,,Letting them provoke us \Ninto infiltrating their base
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.51,0:12:31.67,Italics,Metal,0000,0000,0000,,will only cause more casualties.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.67,0:12:35.02,Italics,Metal,0000,0000,0000,,I won't pointlessly help deal another \Nblow to the Hero Association's forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.48,0:12:38.13,Italics,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to say it like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.13,0:12:40.41,Italics,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,They have a hostage!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.41,0:12:44.28,Main,Metal,0000,0000,0000,,That's the kind of thinking that \Nwill make the situation worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.99,0:12:49.85,Italics,Metal,0000,0000,0000,,If we've tracked down their base, we should \Nforget the operation to save the hostage
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.85,0:12:52.25,Italics,Metal,0000,0000,0000,,and just nuke the whole place.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.25,0:12:55.82,Italics,Metal,0000,0000,0000,,I presented my idea to the Association, \Nbut they turned it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.82,0:12:59.97,Italics,Metal,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently they're more concerned \Nabout their financial situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.59,0:13:05.09,Main,Metal,0000,0000,0000,,Meaning I won't have anything \Nto do with this operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.09,0:13:08.57,Italics,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,And there he goes... \NI swear, he's like a little kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.57,0:13:10.10,sign_18907_225_The_Monster_Asso,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(218,1)}The Monster Association Declares War
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.51,0:13:14.06,Main,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,The masses want to know \Nwhat our next move is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.06,0:13:17.55,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Those bastards leaked this to \Nthe press... Unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.55,0:13:20.32,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Now that the world knows of the \NHero Association's blunder,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.84,0:13:23.44,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,we need to show the world \Njust how ready we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.55,0:13:26.32,sign_18907_225_The_Monster_Asso,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H0E0E10&\3c&H6A6B68&}Monster Association
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.46,0:13:26.32,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The Monster Association, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.73,0:13:30.03,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,They didn't state their location, \Nbut I've got a pretty good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.03,0:13:31.41,sign_19422_233_City_Z_s_hazardo,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,City Z's hazardous area ahead\NAbsolutely no trespassing
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.03,0:13:31.41,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It's in City Z.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.62,0:13:35.45,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,They're planning to start a revolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.45,0:13:39.58,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,This wasn't a message just for the humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.58,0:13:41.40,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It was to summon us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.40,0:13:43.80,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Let's join the Monster Association.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.80,0:13:47.55,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Let's mess those heroes up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.82,0:13:51.84,Main,Sai,0000,0000,0000,,There sure are a lot of \Nmonsters out again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.66,0:13:55.31,Main,Sai,0000,0000,0000,,Did they actually come here to see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.66,0:13:56.81,Main,Sai,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.81,0:13:59.71,Main,Sai,0000,0000,0000,,The garbage truck is gonna \Nshow up any second!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.95,0:14:01.77,Main,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.38,0:14:05.56,Main,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's in our secret base?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.56,0:14:08.57,Main,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Some guy I didn't know \Nwas sleeping in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.57,0:14:09.91,Main,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.36,0:14:13.30,Main,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,Tareo, go check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.30,0:14:14.30,Main,Tareo,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.30,0:14:15.91,Main,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,Tell him what's up, then kick him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.91,0:14:18.61,Main,Tareo,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.61,0:14:20.75,Main,Kid,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, and just go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.42,0:14:22.58,Main,Tareo,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.90,0:14:30.68,Italics,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,My fever's not going down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.57,0:14:36.02,Italics,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, I might not be able to \Nmove much for the next couple of days.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.02,0:14:36.85,Main,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.58,0:14:42.06,Main,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.06,0:14:44.47,Main,Tareo,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This shack is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.73,0:14:48.61,Main,Tareo,0000,0000,0000,,o-our secret... base...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.11,0:14:51.12,Main,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Oh, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.12,0:14:53.66,Main,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,You're the brat that was \Nreading the Hero Guide.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.61,0:14:57.12,Main,Tareo,0000,0000,0000,,You're that old dude!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.12,0:15:00.06,Main,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,Stop calling me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.06,0:15:01.37,Main,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.37,0:15:02.71,Main,Tareo,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.37,0:15:08.53,Main,Tareo,0000,0000,0000,,C-Could you please leave... this shack?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.53,0:15:09.09,Main,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.70,0:15:12.95,Main,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to listen to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.95,0:15:17.85,Main,Tareo,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, the other guys told \Nme to say that to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.85,0:15:20.84,Main,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,Your friends? Just say you don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.84,0:15:22.16,Main,Tareo,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.16,0:15:24.17,Main,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,Stop crying. Jeez, you're annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.06,0:15:29.85,Main,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I won't be here too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.46,0:15:32.36,Main,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,If you've still got a problem,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.78,0:15:35.14,Main,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,bring your friends here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.14,0:15:36.96,Main,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,Got it, you dumb brat?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.96,0:15:38.46,Main,Tareo,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.11,0:15:44.66,Main,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't I give you some good advice
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.23,0:15:47.55,Main,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,to stop people from making fun of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.55,0:15:48.77,Main,Tareo,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.77,0:15:50.63,Main,Tareo,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I wanna know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.59,0:15:53.84,Main,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Tareo sure is taking his time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.84,0:15:55.92,Main,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if something happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.92,0:15:57.67,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Step back, boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.42,0:16:00.78,Main,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,It's Death Gatling!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.78,0:16:02.35,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.35,0:16:04.69,Main,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Smileman! And even Stinger!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.69,0:16:08.82,Main,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! It's a huge group of heroes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.33,0:16:12.79,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,So the hero hunter we keep \Nhearing about is in that shack?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.79,0:16:13.49,Main,Death,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.06,0:16:16.27,Italics,Death,0000,0000,0000,,The hero hunter Garo...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.27,0:16:19.16,Italics,Death,0000,0000,0000,,Today's the day that we hunt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.48,0:16:22.46,Main,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Is there something in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.98,0:16:25.44,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,There's an extremely dangerous \Nmonster in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.44,0:16:26.88,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and get away from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.81,0:16:29.46,Main,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.46,0:16:30.80,Main,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.80,0:16:33.46,Main,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,What are we gonna do? \NWe sent Tareo in there alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.46,0:16:36.45,Main,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,He should be fine now that \Nthe heroes are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.45,0:16:37.68,Main,Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.34,0:16:42.27,Main,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't want to get bossed around \Nor mocked by the people around you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.49,0:16:45.15,Main,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,you just need to become stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.15,0:16:46.06,Main,Tareo,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.06,0:16:48.82,Main,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,How'd you like that? \NGreat advice, am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.82,0:16:51.15,Main,Tareo,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... you just stated the obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.58,0:16:57.63,Main,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! It should be obvious!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.63,0:16:59.87,Main,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,See? You do get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.83,0:17:03.37,Main,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,Laughing makes my wounds hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.78,0:17:05.45,Main,Tareo,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, old dude?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.45,0:17:09.72,Main,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about me. \NMore importantly, you should head home.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.72,0:17:11.34,Main,Tareo,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.50,0:17:14.91,Main,Red,0000,0000,0000,,The door's opening.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.91,0:17:15.68,Main,Death,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.68,0:17:18.68,Main,Death,0000,0000,0000,,The second we see any part of him,\Nwe all fire at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.77,0:17:20.72,Italics,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,We're surrounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.72,0:17:21.63,Main,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.79,0:17:26.65,Main,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,Since I gave you such good advice, \Nyou should show me the Hero Guide in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.65,0:17:27.69,Main,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,You have it, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.85,0:17:31.53,Main,Tareo,0000,0000,0000,,I do... but why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.53,0:17:33.38,Main,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,Because I need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.38,0:17:35.15,Main,Tareo,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.15,0:17:36.22,Main,Tareo,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.38,0:17:36.86,sign_25304_322_Hero_Guide,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(424,1)}Hero\NGuide
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.86,0:17:42.08,Main,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,So this thing has info on \Nall the heroes, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.08,0:17:45.33,Main,Tareo,0000,0000,0000,,Well, not all of them, but yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.33,0:17:46.71,Main,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
