Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.78,0:18:02.51,sign_7523_72_Class_B_Rank_3_W,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\pos(160,20)\fs16}Class {\fs26}B {\fs16}Rank {\fs26}43 Blam-Blam
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.59,0:18:02.51,Italics,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,And one to each side...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.51,0:18:03.97,Italics,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,So a total of eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.50,0:18:07.02,Italics,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,Under normal circumstances, \Nthey'd be easy to take care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.02,0:18:09.10,Italics,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm covered in wounds...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.75,0:18:12.88,Italics,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,Thankfully, there's actually some \Nuseful information in this guide.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.93,0:18:17.13,Main,Tareo,0000,0000,0000,,There's someone outside, old dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.13,0:18:18.24,Main,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk to me right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.24,0:18:20.53,Main,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,Tch. There's no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.66,0:18:25.79,Main,Death,0000,0000,0000,,Get out here, hero hunter.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.61,0:18:28.37,Main,Death,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you know we're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.46,0:18:32.71,Main,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, dumb brat, take cover on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.11,0:18:35.26,Main,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.26,0:18:36.57,Main,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,So don't shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.31,0:18:42.85,Main,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,Please, don't shoot the shack.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.85,0:18:45.06,Main,Stinger,0000,0000,0000,,Cooperating just like that? \NAre you giving up?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.06,0:18:46.37,Main,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.89,0:18:51.15,Main,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,I just don't want to lose the comfy bed \NI come back to after I hunt you all down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.15,0:18:53.11,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to hunt us?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.11,0:18:55.85,Main,Death,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let him rile you up, Wildhorn.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.85,0:18:58.11,Main,Death,0000,0000,0000,,You seemed to be weakened.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.11,0:19:00.41,Main,Death,0000,0000,0000,,We're taking you back \Nto the Association alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.80,0:19:05.29,Main,Death,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to make you spill your \Nmotives and reveal any co-conspirators.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.29,0:19:07.47,Main,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,Spoken like a true hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.47,0:19:10.12,Main,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,How kind of you not to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.43,0:19:13.05,Main,Tareo,0000,0000,0000,,Wow... Heroes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.05,0:19:14.92,Main,Tareo,0000,0000,0000,,They're all really awesome ones, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.92,0:19:18.78,Main,Death,0000,0000,0000,,Don't assume you're in the clear yet. \NWe're not letting you off the hook.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.78,0:19:22.09,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We'll make you regret \Ncalling yourself a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.09,0:19:23.60,Main,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,Same goes for you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.60,0:19:25.97,Main,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,You'll pay big for calling yourself heroes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.38,0:19:40.61,Main,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,Once I eliminate you guys, \NI've officially hunted over a hundred heroes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.61,0:19:42.61,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You're finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.79,0:19:46.87,Main,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,You're first!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.54,0:19:52.30,Italics,Sting,0000,0000,0000,,He dodged that midair? Holy crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.30,0:19:53.78,Italics,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,That was close...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.78,0:19:56.33,Italics,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,That thrust definitely wasn't \Nmeant to take me in alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.96,0:19:58.03,Italics,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,Raining arrows?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.92,0:20:02.27,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,He figured out my attack even \Nthough I'm not that famous...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.27,0:20:06.14,Italics,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,Those are poisonous arrows... \NGlad I read the guide.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.14,0:20:10.85,Main,Tareo,0000,0000,0000,,Why are the heroes attacking him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.17,0:20:13.65,Main,Frog,0000,0000,0000,,He's resisting to the end, despite these odds.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.96,0:20:16.21,Main,Frog,0000,0000,0000,,Is that hero hunter just a fool?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.21,0:20:17.55,Main,Glass,0000,0000,0000,,Chain Toad,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.55,0:20:20.65,Main,Glass,0000,0000,0000,,Tank-Top Master and Metal Bat were \Nboth severely injured by him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.47,0:20:24.78,Main,Glass,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't forget how we \Ntalked about taking him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.78,0:20:28.37,Main,Frog,0000,0000,0000,,To never let our guard down. I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.37,0:20:30.16,Main,Frog,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to show any mercy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.09,0:20:46.45,Main,Smile,0000,0000,0000,,There's no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.45,0:20:48.58,Main,Smile,0000,0000,0000,,He's definitely Silverfang's student.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.58,0:20:49.97,Main,Frog,0000,0000,0000,,Guess he's not just some idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.30,0:20:52.10,Main,Frog,0000,0000,0000,,He's got some crazy instincts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.90,0:20:57.83,Italics,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,At mid-range, Chain Toad and \NSmileman attack endlessly...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.55,0:21:04.23,Main,Arrow,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! I got him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.23,0:21:08.28,Italics,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,But if I move too far away, \NShooter and Blam-Blam shoot me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.83,0:21:10.70,Italics,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,I guess Death Gatling is the end boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.45,0:21:14.78,Italics,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,Also... what the hell has \Nthat guy been doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.78,0:21:15.42,Main,Glasses,0000,0000,0000,,Shooter!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.92,0:21:16.54,Main,Shooter,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.54,0:21:18.25,Italics,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,So he's the support?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.58,0:21:22.06,Italics,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,They've got me marked from all angles.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.06,0:21:22.96,Italics,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.17,0:21:27.09,Main,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make you my shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.09,0:21:27.76,Main,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,You won't get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.30,0:21:29.41,Italics,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.01,0:21:32.64,Italics,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,If I let my guard down any more, \Nhe'll shoot me from behind aga—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.77,0:21:35.85,Italics,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,This little shit...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.57,0:21:40.73,Main,Glasses,0000,0000,0000,,It's also my job to take you \Ndown if you try to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.27,0:21:44.24,Main,Glasses,0000,0000,0000,,I won't lose to anyone when it \Ncomes to stamina or persistence.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.97,0:21:48.32,Main,Glasses,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how long you'll last \Nwith those poison arrows in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.32,0:21:51.08,Main,Glasses,0000,0000,0000,,And CQC is their job.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.73,0:21:57.19,Italics,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,I definitely don't have enough strength \Nto run through all of them right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.19,0:22:01.09,Italics,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,Also, like I could actually dodge \Nbullets, arrows, a chain sickle,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.09,0:22:03.99,Italics,Garo,0000,0000,0000,,and a kendama in my condition!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.99,0:22:07.97,Main,Death,0000,0000,0000,,This is your last chance to surrender, Garo!
